{"id":4025,"date":"2025-06-11T11:14:16","date_gmt":"2025-06-11T04:14:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4025"},"modified":"2025-06-11T11:14:16","modified_gmt":"2025-06-11T04:14:16","slug":"toi-thang-co-nen-nan-mun-khong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/toi-thang-co-nen-nan-mun-khong\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u1edbi th\u00e1ng c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>T\u1edbi th\u00e1ng c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n hay kh\u00f4ng? <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u201c\u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf\u201d th\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00e9o theo s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00e1ng gh\u00e9t. Khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ecb em b\u0103n kho\u0103n c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 m\u1ee5n g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb7n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, n\u1ebfu nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n ch\u01b0a kh\u00f4 c\u1ed3i, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m l\u00e2y lan vi khu\u1ea9n. Khi\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. V\u1eady t\u1ea1i sao m\u1ee5n l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong chu k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t. C\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-gay-mun-trong-ky-kinh-nguyet\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chu k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1 trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng. Lo\u1ea1i hormone progesterone k\u00edch th\u00edch tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u tr\u00ean da t\u0103ng cao. Khi d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u00e0 vi khu\u1ea9n, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4027\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4027\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4027\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-1.webp\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4027\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 hormone, c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ecba m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t. B\u1edfi h\u1ec7 n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1c nhau. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u1ecb em c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i hormone. Trong khi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c \u00edt b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m sau khi chu k\u1ef3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Khi hormone tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. Tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, gi\u00fap h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ee5n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"kinh-nguyet-va-mun-co-nen-nan-mun-trong-nhung-ngay-nay\"><\/span><b>Kinh nguy\u1ec7t v\u00e0 m\u1ee5n: C\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t, l\u00e0n da ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n do t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a hormone. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ecb em b\u0103n kho\u0103n: C\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kinh nguy\u1ec7t ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro cho l\u00e0n da. Nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o th\u00e2m. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u nh\u1eefng nguy c\u01a1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"rui-ro-khi-nan-mun-trong-ky-kinh-nguyet\"><\/span><b>R\u1ee7i ro khi n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-da-kich-ung-sung-viem-nang-hon\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u201c\u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf\u201d, hormone thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u00e0m da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. N\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n ch\u01b0a ch\u00edn. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m v\u1ee1 \u1ed5 vi\u00eam, khi\u1ebfn v\u00f9ng da xung quanh b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u01b0ng t\u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u1eedng \u0111\u1ecf k\u00e9o d\u00e0i.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tang-nguy-co-nhiem-trung-va-lay-lan-mun\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng v\u00e0 l\u00e2y lan m\u1ee5n<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0M\u1ee5n th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ee9a vi khu\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, vi khu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e2y lan sang c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng da kh\u00e1c, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n m\u1ecdc nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu tay ho\u1eb7c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ea1ch, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0a th\u00eam vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0o da, l\u00e0m t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4028\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4028\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4028\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-2.webp\" alt=\"T\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng v\u00e0 l\u00e2y lan m\u1ee5n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4028\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>T\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng v\u00e0 l\u00e2y lan m\u1ee5n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n sai c\u00e1ch, da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e2u h\u01a1n, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh s\u1eb9o th\u00e2m, s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da y\u1ebfu ho\u1eb7c d\u1ec5 t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1, v\u1ebft th\u00e2m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n da b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec nguy c\u01a1 nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng v\u00e0 l\u00e2y lan m\u1ee5n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 n\u1ebfu n\u1eb7n sai c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 ko \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u00f4 khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy c\u01a1 tr\u00ean s\u1ebd n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t da s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a da y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n .<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-cham-qua-trinh-phuc-hoi-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m ch\u1eadm qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t, da \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0nh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Vi\u1ec7c n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e2u l\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. K\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn da y\u1ebfu \u0111i tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khi-nao-co-the-nan-mun\"><\/span><b>Khi n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4029\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4029\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4029\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-3.webp\" alt=\"Khi n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4029\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Khi n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n?<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00edn (\u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n tr\u1ed3i l\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n vi\u00eam s\u01b0ng).<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m do \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn spa ho\u1eb7c c\u01a1 s\u1edf da li\u1ec5u uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da. Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean t\u1ef1 n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u1ea5y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cham-soc-da-thoi-ky-%e2%80%9cden-do%e2%80%9d-dung-cach-%e2%80%93-bi-quyet-de-da-luon-khoe-dep\"><\/span><b>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u201c\u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch &#8211; B\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1eady l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4030\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4030\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4030\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-4.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u201c\u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4030\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u201c\u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf\u201d \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duy-tri-do-am-cho-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, d\u1ec5 kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y:<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> D\u00f9ng serum c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc, kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m v\u00e0 gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3827\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3827\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3827\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3.webp\" alt=\"U\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3827\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>U\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> B\u1ed5 sung n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch u\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 2\u20132.5 l\u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc\/ng\u00e0y.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m 2\u20133 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tranh-tac-dong-manh-len-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, da r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n:<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n, v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam, nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o,\u00a0 m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n n\u1eb7n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u1eadt l\u00fd, thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng AHA\/BHA nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Lu\u00f4n b\u00f4i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a tia UV.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-san-pham-diu-nhe-lanh-tinh\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u201c\u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf\u201d, da th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y \u01b0u ti\u00ean:<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u hay ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Toner c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH, gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4031\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4031\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4031\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5.webp\" alt=\"D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4031\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da d\u00e0nh cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu l\u00e0n da, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"che-do-an-uong-lanh-manh-giup-da-dep-tu-ben-trong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh gi\u00fap da \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da. Trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t, h\u00e3y:<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng rau xanh, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y t\u01b0\u01a1i, gi\u00e0u vitamin A, C, E gi\u00fap da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ed5 sung th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u Omega-3 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1 h\u1ed3i, h\u1ea1t chia v\u00e0 k\u1ebdm \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam da.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, d\u1ea7u m\u1ee1, n\u1ed9i t\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt v\u00ec ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng ti\u1ebft b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3756\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3756\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3756\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3756\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giu-ve-sinh-da-mat-va-ca-nhan-sach-se\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef v\u1ec7 sinh da m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, d\u1ec5 g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u00e3y:<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch 2 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m, tr\u00e1nh ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Thay v\u1ecf g\u1ed1i, kh\u1ea9u trang th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf vi khu\u1ea9n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi da.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Gi\u1eef t\u00f3c s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f3c ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giam-cang-thang-ngu-du-giac\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch tuy\u1ebfn d\u1ea7u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh, khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1eef t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i:<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Thi\u1ec1n, yoga ho\u1eb7c nghe nh\u1ea1c th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m stress.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 7\u20138 ti\u1ebfng\/ng\u00e0y, tr\u00e1nh th\u1ee9c khuya sau 11 gi\u1edd t\u1ed1i, gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 l\u00e0n da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t, da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n. Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7n ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. H\u00e3y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc. Gi\u1eef tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1, t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn d\u00f9 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o trong th\u00e1ng!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u1eady t\u1ea1i sao m\u1ee5n l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong chu k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t. C\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4026,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4025","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4025","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4025"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4025\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4033,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4025\/revisions\/4033"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4026"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4025"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4025"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4025"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}